00:04:01.009 --> 00:04:07.354
empowers the viewer when they're inspired to go
ahead and do the same thing immediately. You know,

00:04:07.354 --> 00:04:11.259
you can grow up watching films and cartoons and be
like, "I want to do that," and you can, you just

00:04:11.259 --> 00:04:15.673
have to go to school for many, many years, and
then build up a resume and try and make work for

00:04:15.673 --> 00:04:19.832
it, and spend countless hours trying to work on an
independent project yourself, and that's really

00:04:19.832 --> 00:04:25.102
cool, but I'd say it's a big investment to get
there. Tabletop roleplaying, if you watch it and

00:04:25.102 --> 00:04:29.484
you're inspired to do it, you can buy a book
tomorrow, get some friends together, and have the

00:04:29.484 --> 00:04:33.623
same exact experience in your own living room.
Nothing excites me more than going and seeing

00:04:33.623 --> 00:04:39.342
