and abused by the military-industrial complex of

00:21:14.775 --> 00:21:19.736
"Shinryu growing up, and you're not really at fault
for how you turned out." Kefka? Oh, you're just a

00:21:19.736 --> 00:21:28.509
dick. You're just a terrible little clown man. And
you hated him and you loved hating him. So yeah, I

00:21:28.509 --> 00:21:32.687
learned a lot about that type of a villain
archetype, I learned about various ways to tell

00:21:32.725 --> 00:21:36.715
elements of a dark story that can still be
compelling. Even though you're dragging your

00:21:36.715 --> 00:21:40.444
