and be like, "That was really impactful and helped

00:21:40.444 --> 00:21:45.947
"me work out some things I wasn't thinking
about." You're like, "Oh, you're welcome. I'll

00:21:45.979 --> 00:21:47.999
"bill you for the therapy later."

