that can't find other players in their vicinity,

00:32:41.988 --> 00:32:48.784
and when times are hard on a global scale, on a
micro-, local scale just making sure that everyone knows

00:32:48.902 --> 00:32:54.909
that we have a community of Critters around. So
you guys really are the reason that this shit is

00:32:54.909 --> 00:32:58.449
working and becoming so prominent. So thank you,
tremendously.

