as I begin to try and print it out, it was hard to

01:29:55.838 --> 01:30:00.271
tailor the rules, and I decided to make it
something wholly new and my own. So that

01:30:00.271 --> 01:30:04.575
particularly was hard. Back in the day,
I remember very early in my D&amp;D career,

01:30:04.575 --> 01:30:08.922
helping my friend make Ryu as a D&amp;D character,
because he really wanted to play Ryu in D&amp;D.

01:30:08.922 --> 01:30:10.248
We were so dumb.

01:30:10.248 --> 01:30:12.215
(laughter)

01:30:12.215 --> 01:30:17.115
MATT: And it was so broken and stupid, and after a
